ょっと見た感じ今回どこまで許可するか選べるようになったみたいです。","ts":"1596508747.063200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"KsC"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"f8180ec2-097e-4064-a49d-cd6caf136d1b","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"private リポジトリの話ですかね?","ts":"1596509020.063500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"zyEf"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"1ff033e0-ac29-47cc-8c1a-22bb53993d62","type":"message","user":"US90LD360","text":"あ、そうです。publicは元々できたのか。","ts":"1596509228.064900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"4vr"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"ef037e70-0993-44f2-a2ef-faff938cbc5c","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"と言うかできないと CI として使い物にならないはずなんですよね…\n外部の人が出してくれた PR のテストが走らないってなんのための CI なのか、という…","ts":"1596509278.065600","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"sorena","count":1,"users":["U9S4G0LJW"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"b6xDk"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"ec0c865e-387f-40da-bf90-e116a977e24f","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"~Circle CI のことかー！~","ts":"1596509302.066000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"bqD"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"1edc932f-b044-4b08-8d43-72e1ff9ac0e1","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"`pull_request` と似ているけどちょっと違う `pull_request_target` トリガーが追加されたようですね","ts":"1596509454.066600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"rwmk"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"13c18e57-7f95-4cdd-adc4-e555c9948189","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"`pull_request` トリガーは、ref (Git のコミット)が PR してきた相手のがベースになっており、そこを基準に各種自動化スクリプトが実行されると、スクリプトが書き換えられていた場合に危険な処理が走る可能性がある。\n`pull_request_target` トリガーは、ref が PR の元ブランチのベースを指しているので安全。とのこと","ts":"1596509580.068700","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"subara","count":1,"users":["US90LD360"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"NECr"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"cf4b9a37-cf90-4b10-9bde-ec10c27b6a15","type":"message","user":"U7B4ZD49X","text":"（GitHubActionsの日本語Slackにも入ってるけどここのほうがいろんな情報が飛び交っているのは内緒）","ts":"1596509639.069400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"0/2h8"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"3c1f9f2a-64fd-4804-a315-fcb207e42c0c","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"どうして…","ts":"1596509660.069600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"VCu"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"cbdb9337-b44e-4505-86b3-67e9dd72cb99","type":"message","user":"U7B4ZD49X","text":"他のSlack見てると正直コミュニティーってのは難しいんだとつくづく感じますね・・・","ts":"1596509684.070500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"q5HC7"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"b34a7322-7c0f-4acd-ac2d-1e87450dbf94","type":"message","user":"US90LD360","text":"いままでprivate repoだとfork開発でCIとして使えなかったんですよね。。マージしないとactions走らないという。","ts":"1596509754.071600","edited":{"user":"US90LD360","ts":"1596509779.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"pGc=o"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"87b56552-075b-4f8b-bebb-d60af727491f","type":"message","u